rica contents  early career  commerce bancorp  petplan  metro bank  book  other investments  business philosophy  personal life  references early careeredit although known for banking hill’s business outlook has been informed by early encounters with retailing while taking morning classes at wharton hill worked afternoons at a south jersey bank owned by a local car retailer where hill observed the car dealer applying retail principles to banking operations such as late opening hours the job also brought hill into contact with other local retailers including mcdonalds after graduation hill founded a real estate firm to find and develop sites for mcdonalds a task which required hill to drive mcdonalds entrepreneur ray kroc on scouting trips hill claims his experience with mcdonald’s taught him the importance of standardised presentation and scale economies in retailing philadelphia magazine reports that hill’s experience with mcdonald’s led directly to the creation of commerce bank referring to the creation of commerce morton kerr chairman of the board of markeimchalmers inc a south jersey real estate firm and one of the original commerce board members observed “a lot of us knew vernon from being involved in real estate at that time…he was a yearold kid who called about  of us to a meeting in his office ill never forget it he said were going to start a bank and he said wed each have to put up between  and  this was who had that kind of money but hed arranged for all of us to borrow it if you could put up  he got us loans for  only seven of us didnt get up and walk out but we still thought he was crazy” the deal resulted in commerce opening its first branch in marlton new jersey in  commerce bancorpedit commerce bank was notable for its rapid expansion from one branch in  to  branches in  and a deposit base that grew by an average of  per year between  and  against an industry average of  in  according to forbes magazine commerce produced a  annual shareholder return c